import React from 'react';
import { Grid } from '@mui/material';

const Home = () => {
    return (
        <>
           <Grid container spacing={6} justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" sx={{height:"100%"}}>
  
       <Grid xs={10} sx={{bgcolor:"#000000",height:"20%",color:"#ffffff"}}>
     Profile
       </Grid>
       <Grid xs={3} sx={{bgcolor:"#000000",color:"#ffffff",height:"20%"}}>
     Message Center
       </Grid>
       <Grid xs={3} sx={{bgcolor:"#000000",ml:1,color:"#ffffff",height:"20%"}}>
     Files
       </Grid>
       <Grid xs={3} sx={{bgcolor:"#000000",ml:1,color:"#ffffff",height:"20%"}}>
     Order Details
       </Grid>
       <Grid xs={5} sx={{bgcolor:"#000000",ml:1,color:"#ffffff",height:"20%"}}>
     Virtual Appointment
       </Grid>
       <Grid xs={5} sx={{bgcolor:"#000000",ml:1,color:"#ffffff",height:"20%"}}>
     Tryon Appointment
       </Grid>
           </Grid>
        </>
    )
}

export default Home
